dct_title_s: Highways: San Francisco Bay Area, California, 2011
dct_description_sm: This polyline shapefile depicts most highways in the nine county San Francisco Bay Area Region, California and is not meant to be precisely accurate. These data were created from a variety of sources developed over the years, including data from ESRI, the California Department of Transportation, the United States Census Bureau Topologically Integrated Geographic Encoding and Referencing (TIGER/Line) and counties.
dct_rights_sm: This work is in the Public Domain, meaning that it is not subject to copyright.
